name: email-templates
description: Skill dedykowany tworzeniu, dziedziczeniu i testowaniu szablonów e-mail (HTML oraz Plain Text)
topics:
  - email-templates
  - jinja2
  - variable-substitution
  - template-inheritance
  - testing
applyTo:
  - path: "**/templates/**"
  - path: "**/*template*.py"
  - path: "**/test_*template*.py"
  - path: "**/*.html"
languageDetection:
  preferredLanguage: python
  patterns:
    - "render_template"
    - "Jinja2"
    - "HTML"
    - "Template"